<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister Greets Venezuelan Counterpart </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK1102013994 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1503 GMT 10 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1102013994 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


