<DOCNO> FBIS3-28997 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas030_d_94033" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-030 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  14 Feb 1994 </DATE1>

